---
// Root route. The actual home page is the static docs/index.html in publicDir;
// this Astro page inlines the same content at build time using Vite's ?raw
// import, so the dev server and production build serve identical bytes.
//
// Why this file exists: Astro's dev server doesn't auto-fall-back to
// publicDir/index.html for the bare "/" path. Without this route, http://
// localhost:<port>/ would 404 in dev (publicDir's index.html still works in
// production because static hosting resolves /  ->  /index.html on its own).
import homepage from '../../docs/index.html?raw';
---
<Fragment set:html={homepage} />
